replies.body:
{{item:3111}} {{item:3725}} {{item:3143}} {{item:3102}} {{item:3071}} {{item:3153}} 
{{item:3143}} & {{item:3071}}  getting buffed for people like vi.

build any said items in any order you want but blade last or 2nd to last

Dont try to solo carry, try to help your team carry themselves or put the other team behind enough for your team to just win. Focus on getting your team through the early game and then when the laning faze is over be enough of a threat to draw attention away from your other carries (Mid laner and adc). 

my build:
{{item:3707}} or {{item:3714}} 
{{item:3047}} or {{item:3111}} 
{{item:3078}} (Some people recommend {{item:3153}} instead)
{{item:3143}} 
{{item:3102}} 
then either more tank or more dmg depending on the game

This way you are generally tanky while still doing dmg. 

tl;dr Apply pressure early game. Then in team fights initiate, take out a high priority target, peel for the other carries or all of the above.
